703113f-a.original_title: Brooklyn: Bay Ridge Avenue - Narrows Avenue
703113f-a.text:
Bay Ridge Ave., west of Narrows Ave.  At the left foreground, is Narrows Ave.  In the far background, is the Bay Ridge Staten Island Ferry.
May 10, 1929.

P.L. Sperr.
No Reproductions.
